Subject: Automatic reply: Urgent VPO # 36435391
BodyText:
This email originated outside of TD SYNNEX.  Please help keep our organization and partners safe. It's up to us; think before you click.

Thank you for contacting Humanscale!

• New Purchase Orders:
If you submitted a new purchase order, you will receive an order acknowledgement or we will contact you with questions on your order within 2 business days.

• Support Requests:
This inbox does not accept support requests on acknowledged orders or for general information. Please submit a support request through one of the following options:

o Humanscale Support Center (Recommended): Visit https://support.humanscale.com to create a support ticket and select Order Type: Enterprise/Global.

o Email: Email your request to our dedicated support address for Enterprise/Global customers, GlobalSupport@humanscale.com.
